quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  33,31,"Kandi muri mwe uzumvira Allah n’intumwa ye akanakora ibikorwa byiza, tuzamugororera ibihembo byikubye kabiri, kandi (ku mperuka) twanamuteguriye amafunguro meza"
  33,32,"Yemwe bagore b’Umuhanuzi (Muhamadi)! Ntabwo mumeze nk’abandi bagore basanzwe. Niba mwumvira (Allah), muramenye ntimukoroshye amajwi (yanyu, igihe muvugana n’abandi bagabo), kugira ngo ufite uburwayi mu mutima atabifuza; ahubwo mujye muvuga mukoresheje imvugo ziboneye"
  33,33,"Mujye munaguma mu ngo zanyu kandi ntimukagaragaze imitako yanyu nk’uko (abagore bo mu bihe) by’ubujiji babikoraga. Mujye muhozaho amasengesho, mutange amaturo kandi mwumvire Allah n’Intumwa ye. Mu by’ukuri, yemwe bantu bo mu rugo (rw’Intumwa)! Allah arashaka kubakuriraho (ibibi n’ibyaha) ndetse (arashaka) kubasukura byimazeyo"
  33,34,"Munazirikane amagambo ya Allah n’amagambo y’intumwa bisomerwa mu ngo zanyu. Mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ugenzabuhoro, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  33,35,"Mu by’ukuri, Abayisilamu n’Abayisilamukazi, abemera n’abemerakazi, abagabo n’abagore bibombarika (kuri Allah), abagabo n’abagore b’abanyakuri, abagabo n’abagore bihangana, abagabo n’abagore bicisha bugufi, abagabo n’abagore batanga amaturo, abagabo n’abagore basiba (Swawumu), abagabo n’abagore barinda ubwambure bwabo, abagabo n’abagore basingiza Allah kenshi; Allah yabateguriye kuzabababarira ibyaha no kuzabaha igihembo gihambaye (Ijuru)"